S.FORM: Mark Rutte u siwkay niza u pilecuhan ni Mark Rutte i Den Haag nu Netherlands. nalecuhan ciniza i 2 a bulad 14 a demiad 1967 a mihcaan. pahezekay niza i tabakiay a cacudadan nu Leiden (Leiden University ). namaala ku kasedan. micakat u cunli ( Prime Minister) nu Netherlands ayza sa ci Mark Rutte, micakat a demiad sa i 2010 a mihcaan 10 bulad 14 demiad. u ngangan niza u sulit tu ngangan nu Netherlands a kamu:Mark Rutte u sulit tu ngangan nu hulam a kamu: u sulit tu ngangan nu Sakizaya a kamu:Make Lite u sapuyaay a kakuniza kakuniza malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government Mark Rutte
